text: Dave De Ruff (born April 10, 1961) is an American rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:American male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Santa Ana, California
